# Using the package

flet run src/raoc/main.py


# Dev install under linux 

```commandline
sudo apt install libmpv1
```

# Upload to PyPI

```commandline
poetry config pypi-token.pypi your-api-token
```

```commandline
poetry build
poetry publish
```



